  "texts": [
    "Our AI-Reliant Code Generators and Stojanov et al. 's \"task-delegators\" both exhibit a high dependence on ChatGPT, though our profile focuses on direct answers for programming tasks, while theirs extends to drafting and writing assignments.",
    "AI-Reliant Code Generator & Refiners share similarities with \"knowledge seekers\", as both involve refining and seeking explanations, though \"knowledge seekers\" focus more broadly on content acquisition.",
    "AI-Assisted Code Refiners and \"proactive learners\" both use ChatGPT for feedback and optimization, with a notable emphasis on initial independent effort from our AI-Assisted Code Refiners.",
    "Lastly, AI-Collaborative Coders and \"knowledge seekers\" show a targeted approach to using ChatGPT for specific guidance, though \"all-rounders\" exhibit the highest reliance on the tool.",
    "These comparisons underscore the diversity in students' interaction patterns and reliance on AI, reflecting varying degrees of independence and collaboration in task completion."
